SP.P:
No, no, Fighting is not the Vice of these Times;
and as for a little Swaggering—damn it, I can do it as
well as the best of 'em.

O, Sir! My Passion has undone me—I am dis∣cover'd;
it is my Husband, Sir George, and he is
looking for me—

Lord, Sir!—he is the most passionate of Mor∣tals;
and I am afraid is in Liquor too—and then he
is mad.
